The '''Diet of Imperial Planetary Governors''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] organization active by [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]]. Its role was to put a positive spin on Imperial edicts to help forestall popular uprisings.<ref name="Star Wars Handbook 2: Crimson Empire">[[Star Wars Handbook 2: Crimson Empire|''Star Wars Handbook'' 2: ''Crimson Empire'']]</ref>

In 11 ABY, Diet member [[Tann Starpyre]] was placed on the [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends|Interim Ruling Council]] by [[Carnor Jax]] to foster an illusion of representative democracy.<ref name="Star Wars Handbook 2: Crimson Empire" />

